  "texts": [
    "For text processing, BERT employs transformers and masked language modeling.",
    "The main challenge is comprehending the context of the word mentioned in that location.",
    "The pronouns in a phrase can be difficult for the machine to understand.",
    "Transformers can therefore pay attention to pronouns, try the word with the entire sentence, and comprehend the context.",
    "Masked language modeling prevents the target word from comprehending it."
  ],
